{"tid":2038304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙田十三校關注組發起罷課 林大輝中學稱或法律追究學生","createTime":"2020-05-27T13:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T17:20:47.000Z","uid":68824,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"11763a009faf48596ddf644bbcd64fdec1833b94","tid":2038304,"uid":68824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tmhk.org/2020/05/27/沙田十三校關注組發起罷課-林大輝中學稱或法律追/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftmhk.org%2F2020%2F05%2F27%2F%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E6%A0%A1%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2-%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%A7%E8%BC%9D%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%A8%B1%E6%88%96%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E8%BF%BD%2F&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32ZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=9090d33a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tmhk.org/2020/05/27/沙田十三校關注組發起罷課-林大輝中學稱或法律追/</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會今日恢復《國歌條例草案》二讀程序，多個學生團體於復課首日發起罷課，表明的反對《國歌法》及《國安法》。沙田區除了崇真中學及培英中學，有名為「沙燕兒女」的九間中學學生團體聯合發出罷課聲明，並呼籲學生及校友響應。<br />\n<br />\n有發起罷課的林大輝中學本土關注組在昨日得到校方通知，指校方會沿用去年十一月罷課的處理方式，安排持有家長信的學生到特別室自習。有關注組負責人表示今晨學生在校外派發有關罷課的單張，但遭學校職員警告，指其行為影響校譽。<br />\n<br />\n林大輝中學昨日發表聲明譴責發起團隊未經學校授權使用校名，更以學校名義發起未經授權的活動，指會向有關同學保留法律追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n同區梁文燕中學反修例關注組昨日於社交媒體發帖文，指家教會已知悉學生的罷課安排，同時因為關注組成員以中六畢業校生為主，校方可能會阻止他們的成員進入校園。<br />\n<br />\n另外有網民發起早上上班時間在全港的馬路慢駛堵路，意圖逼使上班人士罷工，但早上的沙田區交通正常，有警員駐守地鐵站內外，大部份在大圍站巡邏，亦有警員多度截查年輕市民。"},{"pid":"ba763157551a75aea4530089842845a2fb2a5ba5","tid":2038304,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"關注組應該同校名唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"9293cc6477903cbb679abedb7ab0591e328bb6a0","tid":2038304,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:12:55.000Z","msg":"咁叫非林大輝中學本土關注組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7af004bebe687a3ec06fd5060716789dada9225","tid":2038304,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:19:20.000Z","msg":"不如叫撚大廢中學本土關注組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3caa57fd3ac43c9b25110184bcd8bac5ebe1727","tid":2038304,"uid":68824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba763157551a75aea4530089842845a2fb2a5ba5","tid":2038304,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"關注組應該同校名唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:28:17.000Z","msg":"應該係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6c9db7b7d339630f710ebc1fedc3dafa3f3802","tid":2038304,"uid":173179,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:36:22.000Z","msg":"絕對不是「林大輝中學」罷課關注組囉"},{"pid":"1df936c2d37a9ce352a43cdc6981077ee0c49370","tid":2038304,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"犯法?"},{"pid":"a9c002f420cb38542c03b4646bb05af8203cd0c1","tid":2038304,"uid":68824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1df936c2d37a9ce352a43cdc6981077ee0c49370","tid":2038304,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"犯法?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"要搵個讀law嘅講吓"},{"pid":"1d02e88b9a61a5467d87a5e49988c9a1980d5b8d","tid":2038304,"uid":92038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T14:10:34.000Z","msg":"報警拉學生囉 咁威<br />\n唔報警正垃圾呀契弟<br />\n兇鳩學生都低能"},{"pid":"5bb7ec0acbaa103dc183087687a7e57a99bbd338","tid":2038304,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9c002f420cb38542c03b4646bb05af8203cd0c1","tid":2038304,"uid":68824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1df936c2d37a9ce352a43cdc6981077ee0c49370","tid":2038304,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"犯法?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"要搵個讀law嘅講吓"},